cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.DC

The paper discusses Theano, a popular library for mathematical computation in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), as these are all relevant to the topics covered in the paper.
